description: The index’s initial investible universe consists of equity securities listed on securities exchanges in the U.S., developed markets, and South Korea (the “Universe”). The Advisor attempts to invest all, or substantially all, of its assets in the component securities that make up the index. It may invest in common stocks, partnership interests, business trust shares and other equity investments or ownership interests in business enterprises. The fund’s investments may include small-, medium- and large-capitalization companies.
